experiments.description:
Trained InceptionV3 architecture using the 'Chexpert_CWBCE_E12_B32_C1_N12' benchmark. The benchmark was initialized for the chexpert_preprocessed-256-crop dataset with batch size of 32, shuffle set to True and images rescaled to dimension (256, 256).
The training was done for 12 epochs using the Adam optimizer and weighted_binary_crossentropy loss.
A total of 12 labels/pathologies were included in the training and encoded using the 'uzeroes' method.
The traing set included 142320 number of sample, the validation set 36162, and the test set 44932.

experiments.name: DenseNet121_Chexpert_CWBCE_E10_B32_C1_N13
experiments.description:
Trained DenseNet121 architecture using the 'Chexpert_CWBCE_E10_B32_C1_N13' benchmark. The benchmark was initialized for the chexpert_preprocessed-256-crop dataset with batch size of 32, shuffle set to True and images rescaled to dimension (256, 256).
The training was done for 10 epochs using the Adam optimizer and weighted_binary_crossentropy loss.
A total of 13 labels/pathologies were included in the training and encoded using the 'uzeroes' method.
The traing set included 142320 number of sample, the validation set 36162, and the test set 44932.
